{"tid":1585264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連仔請入]置頂申請/投稿制 有冇得諗?","createTime":"2019-09-21T13:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T14:02:19.000Z","uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64e170ad9e8c366f7fea02591cded4ef1d9d279f","tid":1585264,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n見到好多巴絲都好努力咁秒回po宣傳行動<br />\n但睇怕宣傳成效已經不大<br />\n因為大部分人(包括我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)都會直接飛左佢去睇其他留言<br />\n但唔咁樣bot文宣又會有d活動冇人知(e.g.滙豐果個集會)<br />\n另開一個行動po又會正皮完推完就算 只係熱門留一段好少時間<br />\n(因為活動 twitter戰線等呢d基本上冇咩討論空間 見到就做 推完就算<br />\n相反即時討論果d就因為討論熱烈而會係熱門留好耐)<br />\n<br />\n有見及此<br />\n諗緊不如俾人投稿申請置頂<br />\n宣傳9月10月有咩活動又好  twitter reddit文宣戰線又好<br />\n<strong>俾其他人一禁入去就知要做咩or有咩要做</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以係連仔決定咩置頂 或者有個專區俾大家正負皮決定咩置頂<br />\n可以即日更新置頂 or成個月行動果d俾佢長期置頂 有新野再加入<br />\n細節大家入黎集思廣益下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817c71f811e83121e24d1fa9b1876b4d454ac0f0","tid":1585264,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:55:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45528b431e348e6224109bd03264290ec7c1e733","tid":1585264,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:55:42.000Z","msg":"大家入黎俾我知有冇得諗丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b08f6a41eacf45bde241e94ecc332ec51eb6d7","tid":1585264,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897f8ba66e3eadabbafdbb33241657e59aeb55e5","tid":1585264,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif